<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Agent OS — The AI Command Centre That Runs Your Business</title>
<meta name="description" content="One dashboard. Seven AI agents. Built by Julian Goldie. Get the ready-made setup inside the AI Profit Boardroom." />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bricolage+Grotesque:opsz,wght@12..96,200..800&family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Caveat:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg-deep:    #15101a;
    --bg-mid:     #1c1622;
    --bg-card:    #251d2c;
    --bg-elev:    #2e2436;

    --cream:      #f3ebda;
    --cream-soft: #ddd0bb;
    --cream-dim:  #a59783;
    --cream-mute: #6e6353;

    --gold:       #d4a574;
    --gold-soft:  #e6c69a;
    --gold-deep:  #a87f54;

    --emerald:    #5ab896;
    --plum:       #c4607e;
    --rust:       #c97c5e;

    --line:       rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.20);
    --line-soft:  rgba(243, 235, 218, 0.08);

    --shadow-1: 0 1px 0 rgba(243, 235, 218, 0.03), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    --shadow-2: 0 2px 0 rgba(243, 235, 218, 0.04), 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body {
    background: var(--bg-deep);
    color: var(--cream);
    font-family: 'Manrope', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.65;
    padding-top: 60px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Paper grain */
  body::before {
    content: ""; position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 1;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='200' height='200'><filter id='n'><feTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='2' stitchTiles='stitch'/><feColorMatrix values='0 0 0 0 0.95  0 0 0 0 0.9  0 0 0 0 0.85  0 0 0 0.035 0'/></filter><rect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)'/></svg>");
    opacity: 0.55; mix-blend-mode: overlay;
  }
  /* Ambient glow */
  body::after {
    content: ""; position: fixed; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 65% 45% at 12% 6%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.09), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 40% at 88% 22%, rgba(201, 124, 94, 0.07), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 95%, rgba(196, 96, 126, 0.06), transparent 60%);
  }
  main, .sticky-banner { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

  /* Sticky top banner */
  .sticky-banner {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 60px;
    background: rgba(21, 16, 26, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(14px) saturate(140%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 30px;
    z-index: 50;
  }
  .sticky-banner .left {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--cream-soft);
  }
  .sticky-banner .left .pulse {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--emerald);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--emerald);
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.4} }
  .sticky-banner em {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.4em; color: var(--gold); line-height: 0.9;
  }
  .sticky-banner a.join {
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg-deep);
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 9px 20px; border-radius: 999px; text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .sticky-banner a.join:hover {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  main { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px 120px; }

  /* Chapter eyebrow */
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px; color: var(--cream-dim);
  }
  .eyebrow .num {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.55rem; color: var(--gold); line-height: 0.9;
  }
  .eyebrow .line { width: 36px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); opacity: 0.6; }
  .eyebrow .label {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.24em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
  }

  /* Headings */
  h1, h2, h3 {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.032em;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.04;
  }
  h1 { font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.6rem); margin: 18px 0 28px; }
  h2 { font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.2rem); margin: 12px 0 22px; }
  h3 { font-size: 1.55rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0 0 12px; }
  h1 em, h2 em, h3 em {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.18em; line-height: 0.9;
  }

  /* Paragraphs */
  p { font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--cream-soft); margin-bottom: 18px; }
  p.lead { font-size: 1.22rem; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 30px; }
  p .hand {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 0.85;
  }

  code, .mono { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace; }
  code {
    font-size: 0.92em; color: var(--gold-soft);
    background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Section spacing + dividers */
  section { margin: 90px 0; }
  section:first-of-type { margin-top: 60px; }
  .divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px; margin: 110px 0;
  }
  .divider .rule { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--line); max-width: 180px; }
  .divider .ornament {
    color: var(--gold); opacity: 0.7;
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  /* Pull quotes */
  blockquote {
    margin: 50px 0; padding: 0 0 0 30px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.018em;
  }
  blockquote cite {
    display: block; margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--gold); font-style: normal;
  }

  /* Hero image card */
  .hero-shot {
    margin: 50px 0 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2);
    background: var(--bg-card);
    position: relative;
  }
  .hero-shot img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
  .hero-shot::after {
    content: ""; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(21, 16, 26, 0.5), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .shot-caption {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cream-mute);
  }
  .shot-caption em {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.5em; color: var(--gold); margin: 0 4px;
  }

  /* Pillar grid */
  .pillars {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 22px; margin: 40px 0;
  }
  .pillar {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 22px 22px 24px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .pillar:hover { border-color: var(--line); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .pillar .num {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 2rem; color: var(--gold); line-height: 0.9; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .pillar h3 {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.18rem; letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .pillar p {
    font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--cream-soft); margin: 0;
  }

  /* Inline metric strip */
  .metric-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
    gap: 28px;
    margin: 36px 0;
    padding: 28px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
  }
  .metric-strip .item .label {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.66rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--cream-mute);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .metric-strip .item .value {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.15rem; letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .metric-strip .item .value em {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.5em; line-height: 0.9; margin-right: 4px;
  }

  /* Big CTA card */
  .cta-card {
    margin: 70px 0;
    padding: 50px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08), rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.02));
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2);
  }
  .cta-card .eyebrow { justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .cta-card h2 { font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .cta-card p { max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 28px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .cta-card a.btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg-deep);
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 16px 38px; border-radius: 999px; text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
  }
  .cta-card a.btn:hover {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.35);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .cta-card .micro {
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-mute);
  }

  /* Comparison list (✓ / ✗) */
  .checklist { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 24px 0; }
  .checklist li {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    font-size: 1.02rem; color: var(--cream-soft);
  }
  .checklist li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .checklist li .check {
    flex-shrink: 0; width: 18px; height: 18px; margin-top: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%; display: grid; place-items: center;
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .checklist li.yes .check { background: rgba(90, 184, 150, 0.18); color: var(--emerald); }
  .checklist li.no  .check { background: rgba(196, 96, 126, 0.18); color: var(--plum); }
  .checklist li b { color: var(--cream); font-weight: 600; }

  /* Author block */
  .author {
    display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 32px;
    margin: 60px 0;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .author .avatar {
    width: 64px; height: 64px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold), var(--rust));
    color: var(--bg-deep);
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .author h4 {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .author .role {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .author p { font-size: 0.95rem; margin: 0; color: var(--cream-soft); }

  /* Final close section */
  .final-close {
    margin: 100px 0 40px;
    padding: 70px 40px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.15), transparent 60%),
      var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(243, 235, 218, 0.08);
  }
  .final-close h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
  }
  .final-close p { max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 30px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .final-close .promise {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold); font-size: 2rem;
    margin: 30px 0 14px;
  }

  /* Inline pricing chip */
  .pricing-chip {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 6px;
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(90, 184, 150, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 184, 150, 0.4);
    color: var(--emerald);
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  ul.body-list {
    list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 18px 0 24px;
  }
  ul.body-list li {
    position: relative; padding-left: 22px; margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 1.04rem; color: var(--cream-soft); line-height: 1.55;
  }
  ul.body-list li::before {
    content: "✦"; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 2px;
    color: var(--gold); font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* Responsive 16:9 YouTube embed in the same card frame as hero-shot */
  .video-shot {
    position: relative;
    margin: 50px 0 14px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2);
    background: #000;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
  }
  .video-shot iframe {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    border: 0; display: block;
  }

  /* Section CTA — every CTA on the page uses this same beautiful card style
     with the big gold pill button. Compact version of .cta-card, but visually
     just as strong. Headline + sub + button + micro text. */
  .section-cta {
    display: block;
    margin: 50px 0 14px;
    padding: 36px 32px 32px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08), rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.02));
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;          /* nukes browser default blue link colour */
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-1);
    transition: border-color 0.25s, transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s, background 0.25s;
  }
  .section-cta:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 44px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.2), var(--shadow-1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.12), rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.04));
  }
  .section-cta .head {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.55rem; letter-spacing: -0.018em;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 8px;
    line-height: 1.18;
  }
  .section-cta .head em {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.35em; line-height: 0.9; margin: 0 2px;
  }
  .section-cta .sub {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.92rem; line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--cream-soft);
    max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 22px;
  }
  .section-cta .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg-deep);
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.86rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 15px 36px; border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .section-cta:hover .pill {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.35);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .section-cta .micro {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-mute);
  }

  /* Hero CTA — the one above the fold, even punchier */
  .hero-cta {
    margin: 24px 0 14px;
    padding: 32px 32px 30px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 20%, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.18), transparent 70%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.08), rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.02));
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2);
    transition: transform 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 56px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.28), var(--shadow-2);
  }
  .hero-cta .head {
    font-family: 'Bricolage Grotesque', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.7rem; letter-spacing: -0.018em;
    color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.18;
  }
  .hero-cta .head em {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; font-style: normal; font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.35em; line-height: 0.9; margin: 0 2px;
  }
  .hero-cta .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gold); color: var(--bg-deep);
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.94rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 17px 42px; border-radius: 999px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    transition: background 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover .pill {
    background: var(--gold-soft);
    box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .hero-cta .micro {
    margin-top: 14px;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream-mute);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    body { padding-top: 56px; }
    .sticky-banner { padding: 0 16px; }
    .sticky-banner .left { font-size: 12px; gap: 8px; }
    .sticky-banner a.join { padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; }
    main { padding: 0 18px 80px; }
    section { margin: 60px 0; }
    .cta-card, .final-close { padding: 36px 22px; }
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- ============ STICKY BANNER ============ -->
<div class="sticky-banner">
  <div class="left">
    <span class="pulse"></span>
    The full <em>Agent OS</em> setup lives inside the AI Profit Boardroom
  </div>
  <a class="join" href="https://www.skool.com/ai-profit-lab-7462/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join</a>
</div>

<main>

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section style="margin-top: 64px;">
  <div class="eyebrow">
    <span class="num">I.</span>
    <span class="line"></span>
    <span class="label">The Sovereign Stack</span>
  </div>

  <h1>One command centre. <em>Seven</em> AI agents. Zero chaos.</h1>

  <p class="lead">
    Most people are stuck in one chat window, tinkering with AI like it's 2023.
    Meanwhile, a few of us built our own operating system — every agent, every
    memory, every signal in one beautiful dashboard. This is what it looks like
    when you stop tinkering and start <em>running</em> AI like a real business.
  </p>

  <div class="metric-strip">
    <div class="item"><div class="label">Agents wired in</div><div class="value"><em>7</em></div></div>
